    "description": [
      "We sincerely apologise, we had some serious issues with the last build.If anyone purchased Arcade mode and is being asked to buy it again please use the Restore Purchases button we've just added. In testing it sometimes took a few tries to successfully restore, but I believe this has to do with waiting till Google Play has responded that it is ready to purchase. Playing a round of Classic mode will probably give it enough time to set itself up and should then work the first time.Have fun with the free credits and jump over to our Facebook page and tell us which Perk you like the most, or even make some suggestions for new ones.Here it is! Version 2.5In celebration of Photon reaching 250 000 downloads this update includes 10,000 free Atoms to use on Perks in Arcade mode. Thanks to everyone for helping to make Photon a success, and a huge thank you for the constructive feedback we've received.Also in this version:- Improved tilt control (including the ability to calibrate your device).\n- Added Colour Blind Assist (The \"eye\" icon in the menu).\n- Fixed a few gameplay bugs.\n- Automatically saves Audio, Tilt and ColourBlind Assist preferences between plays.\n- Improved stability, should be a lot less crashing happening.\n- Temporarily disable OpenFeint. It was responsible for many of the freezes and crashes.A huge thank you to all those players who love Photon and have given us a good rating, we greatly appreciate your support.Feel free to join in any discussions, or create new ones, on our Facebook page www.Facebook.com/BifrostStudios or follow us on twitter @BifrostStudiosNew in Version 2.0- Lots of bug fixes\n- Screen flicker glitch fixed\n- Fixed all known game crashing bugs\n- Enabled OpenFeint for Android users\n- Added a skip tutorial button\n- Added The NEW Arcade mode\n- So many gameplay enhancements (the game is 100 times more fun now)\n- Graphics update (so many high visuals)NEW GAME MODE ADDED\n- Arcade Mode, is a fast paced countdown mode allowing the player to achieve scores of 100000+. Using unlockable perks and entering Fusion mode players will see combos out of this world.- Earn Atoms be RICH!\n- Enter Fusion mode for a psychedelic experience\n- Connect multi colour combos with the New Bridge DiskPhoton! Exciting disc game! Connect discs - now they are destroyed! Longer chains will impress your friend! Special discs make life hard for you - include them in combos to get terrific bonus points! All graphics are next level! You must have quick brain and fast eyes! Do not panic! The future is here! Play it now for free! We are aware of a few issues, an update is on its way!"
    ],
