    "description": [
      "ZEEBOX TAKES TV WATCHING TO NEW LEVELS - it's social, informational, clever and fun.\nzeebox does not replace your TV\nzeebox DOES act as your TV’s sidekick by helping you discover new shows, learn more about shows you already love, stay connected to social buzz, offers up content to share and interact with... all live as you watch and without having to leave the app. Best of all: it's totally FREE!WHAT’S NEW:\n*Find other fans of the shows you watch by checking out their profile pages. Click on any zeeboxer to check out the shows they're watching, booking, talking about and more. With zeebox, you’ll never have to watch your favorite shows alone.*Comcast XFINITY subscribers can find a show and switch to the channel it is playing on directly from zeebox on their Android device.*'TV Picks' on zeebox shows you which US TV shows are the most buzzed about at any moment. You can also see what just your friends or favorite celebrities are watching at a glance.*You’ll never miss out on your favorite shows when you use the zeebox 'Book to Watch' feature. Just click the icon on the show page and zeebox will send you a reminder before your show starts. You can also see your friends’ bookings as well as the Top 10 most booked shows at any time.*Get Social – TV is more fun with friends (or strangers, your choice). Start your own chat room on zeebox and let the conversation begin. Whether you want to privately chat with friends or open up the discussion to the public, the zeebox chat feature acts as your virtual living room. Not in the mood for long-form discussions but have something you want to Tweet out? You can post to your Twitter feed without leaving the app. You’re in control of how ‘social’ you want to be… and with whom.*Find out more about what's on screen with our live zeetags. Click one for instant info - or to buy what's on screen.*Don’t just watch – interact. Play along with your favorite shows in fun new ways with games, live polls, voting and experiences you won’t find anywhere else.WHAT THEY'RE SAYING ABOUT ZEEBOX\n\"…it pulls together all the second-screen chatter for you, right before your eyes\" - Fast Company\n\"zeebox is going to change the way you watch your favorite TV shows\" - E! Online\n\"If you watch TV regularly, zeebox is an excellent companion\" - CNET\n\"The app for the TV obsessed\" - Forbes\n\"I've seen the future of TV, and its name is zeebox\" - paidContent"
    ],
