    "description": [
      "The improved My FiOS App has new features built in, giving you easy access to your Verizon account, email messages, support and access to the new FiOS Mobile application for all your FiOS TV entertainment. VIEW AND PAY YOUR BILL NOW OR LATER. ANYTIME, ANYWHERE\nRest easy knowing your bill is always up-to-date from anywhere. View recent payments, set up a new payment and even sign up for paperless billing in just a few simple steps. VERIZON EMAIL\nThe My FiOS App enables you to send and receive emails from your Verizon account. FiOS TV\nCheck out the new Verizon FiOS Mobile application with favorite live streaming TV Channels, available now to watch anywhere in your home! FiOS Mobile also offers premium subscription On Demand content from Starz and Encore, the ability to use your device as a remote control to interact with your FiOS TV, remotely manage your DVR recordings, view TV listings and access loads of Flex View On Demand titles (Flex View titles only available on select Android devices).HOME MONITORING AND CONTROL. NOW IN YOUR POCKET\nConnect to the most important place on earth directly from your mobile device. On vacation? With the My FiOS App and Home Monitoring and Control**, you can switch on the lights to look like you’re home, check things out with a live video feed, and so much more! GET SUPPORT FROM YOUR PHONE.\nThe My FiOS App provides Support help enhanced with Speech Recognition capabilities to take you to the information you need with an option to reach out to the regular Verizon Support Centers. Type or speak your question and get support information and tools for your Verizon services.\nAnd so much more! ** Home Monitoring and Control Service is provided by Verizon Online LLC. Licensed in NY # 12000302262 by NY State Department of State. VA DJCS #11-6657.\nNOTE: If your device is running Android 4.2 or newer and the authenticated functions don't seem to work, please make sure you upgrade ALL Verizon apps (My FiOS, FiOS Mobile, FiOS Digital Voice & Home Control) in order to ensure that your credentials are saved properly"
    ],
