    "description": [
      "Earth 2050. A year has passed since hostile aliens arrived to destroy the human race. So far, the invaders have been pushed back by cybernetic mech soldiers programmed at the Robot Academy. Now, you will take charge of the Robot Academy initiative and shoulder the responsibility of Earth’s safety! The nations of Earth have collaborated to establish the finest training academies for the mechanized infantry forces that protect us against the alien threat. Welcome to the Robot Academy, professor! Your job is to make sure that our best and finest Robot Troopers are well-trained, well-equipped, and well-oiled. Countless alien forces stream out from each starship with the sole intent to wipe out the human race. Can you help turn the tide of battle, or will this be the end of our civilization? GAMEPLAY\nAcademies churn out the vast numbers of Robot Troopers needed to combat the alien threat. You will manage each academy by assigning robots and androids to the appropriate combat and tactics courses and directing service droids to program and maintain them. There are various academies located across the globe and it is imperative that they all operate at peak efficiency. Your efforts on the assembly line will determine the outcome of space battles against the aliens, so keep producing Robot Troopers efficiently and we may have a chance of winning this war! FEATURES\n- Addictive sci-fi themed strategy and time management gameplay\n- 9 exciting, futuristic levels\n- 8 Robot staff to hire and train: Zen, R2B2, Pixel, Mac, Mech, Archie, Tech, Jarvis\n- 5 consumable boosters to help you advance in the game - Cash Magnet, Wild Card, Speed Boost, Music Box, and Door Blocker\n- Awesome mech designs\n- 9 different academies located in various secret locations\n- 9 specialized droids ready to train recruits\n- Install and upgrade the academy's equipment to improve speed and efficiency\n- Complete various production goals to earn bonuses\n- Earn daily rewards\n- Collect the tokens to play the slot machine to earn bonus rewards.** Please note that while the app is free, please be aware that it contains paid content for real money that can be purchased upon users' wish to enhance their gaming experience. You can disable in-app purchases by adjusting your device’s settings. **"
    ],
