    "description": [
      "Alerts & Deals is a free app from Smoopa that helps you discover great deals online. Join forces with fellow shoppers to find and share good prices. Buy it now or get alerted when the price drops even further.\"Bargain hunters have never had it better.\"\n- The Wall Street Journal\"Smoopa factors in shipping costs too, so a buyer can tell whether the overall price will be better offline or online.\"\n- TechCrunch\"Smoopa always includes shipping costs in its prices\"\n- All Things DigitalHow do I share a deal?\nUse the app to browse for deals and when you find one you like, tap on Like to share it with others.Can I search for items?\nYes, you can tap on the search icon in the upper right corner to search for items by name and see which retailer has the lowest price. We'll also show you historical prices to help you decide whether to buy it now or later.Are shipping costs included?\nYes, shipping costs are always included so you can easily compare prices across retailers. What are some online retailers to which you compare prices?\nWe are constantly adding more retailers to our database and currently compare prices with online retailers such as Amazon, Walmart, Target, Best Buy, and Macy's. When Smoopa finds you a lower price and you complete your purchase, Smoopa may be compensated by the online retailer.What happens when I sign up for alerts?\nIf you're not ready to make a purchase, you can sign up for alerts and we will send you an email when the online price drops below your alert price.Fan Feedback\n\"Awesome! This app is amazing. Love it.\"\n\"Great idea, great execution! The items and deals are relevant and not a bunch of fodder like similar websites I've seen. It's addicting to browse randomly just to see if you find a sweet deal you can't pass up on :)\"\n\"Love shopping! Especially when this application allows u to buy at the right time! Big money saver!\"\n\"I've only had this app for a couple of weeks and I have been able to find several great deals that worked for me. Excellent.\"\n\"I love the app! Great design.\"\n\"Love and way I can save money! It works great too!!! 5 stars from the Williams family!!!!\""
    ],
