      "* Play the world’s #1 hit Time Management Cooking game on your Android!Cook up culinary chaos! With over 20 million downloads to date, Dash is one of the biggest mobile gaming franchises ever! Cooking Dash delivers fast-paced, addicting fun that’s perfect for playing on-the-go! Keep customers happy by prepping everything from burgers and fries to sushi and dumplings. Tap and slide to seat customers, serve up piping hot dishes, and collect big tips! Help our heroine Flo keep DinerTown’s restaurants up and running... if you can stand the heat! GAME FEATURES: * Play a variety of uniquely fun gourmet restaurants, including the FREE Potsticker Palace!\n* Enjoy tons of exciting levels that’ll keep you on your toes\n* Prepare delicious cuisine from all around the world, including Japanese, Italian and more!\n* Shop for speed boosts, super-charged appliances, and brilliant decor upgrades\n* Serve fun and familiar customers, from yoga instructors to body builders Love the fast-paced fun of Cooking Dash? Try Diner Dash, another addicting PlayFirst game on Google Play. You’re guaranteed to see familiar faces you know and love!*******************\nWant more from PlayFirst? Facebook:\n http://www.facebook.com/playfirstgames Twitter: @playfirst Blog:\n http://blog.playfirst.com"
