    "description": [
      "A beautiful 3D live wallpaper background of a flag blowing in the wind! Not a movie, this wallpaper has full support for home screen changing and landscape mode, and will work both on phones and tablets! Works as a Daydream on supported devices!If you enjoy this, please support us by getting the full version! It contains North American flags from USA, Canada, Mexico, Greenland, 50 US states, DC, Guam, and Puerto Rico! Or create your own flag, if you want! Multiple flag styles, backgrounds, custom backgrounds, and lots more settings!TO USE: Long-press on your home screen for the Live Wallpapers list!While we appreciate everyone's enthusiasm, there's no need for controversy. The United States Flag Code states that the union (the starfield) part of the flag should be displayed in the upper left. The treatment of the flag in this wallpaper is analogous to a wall display, so this rule applies. Please see the article here: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States_Flag_Code"
    ],
