    "description": [
      "OMG, the day is getting hotter and hotter, it's time for us to wear the beautiful sandals and show out our pretty toenails!!!\nGirls, if you are really crazy about toenail design, if you are really expected to have various toenail decorations, if you are really excited to see so many toenail polishes, you'll absolutely love our Toenail Salon! Here you can do everything you ever imagined about your toenails, so don't hesitate any more, join the Toenail Salon, enjoy a shining and colorful summer!\nHow to play:\nIn our Toenail Salon, you can just tap a toe to zoom in on it and start designing your own nail art! Here you can choose from plenty of polish colors, many decorative patterns, tons of sparkling rhinestones, crystals, diamonds, gemstones, pearls, fimo, resin and so on to decorate your toenails. You can apply a different design to each nail or tap the \"Apply to All“ button to use the current design to all toes! Besides, you can also choose a more convenient way, for we have already designed some artistic toenail sets for you, just click your favorite set then have a rest and enjoy your bling toenails! After decorating your toenails , you can put a unique tattoo on your feet, then wear a pair of beautiful sandal, which will make your toenail design more attractive! At last, you can either take a photo with your toenails as our cover girl, or share your works and happiness with your friends through E-mail or Facebook.\nFeatures: * Various backgrounds available to switch\n * Four different skin tones\n * 22 tat toos for you to put on your feet\n * 25 anklets for you to choose\n * 53 finished artistic toenail sets to choose from\n * 25 sandals to try on\n * Plentiful nail polish colors to choose\n * 41 toenail decorative patterns\n * Sparkling crystals, diamonds, and gemstones to use\n * Cute fimo & resin\n * Gorgeous gem alloy\n * Design each toenail differently or simply apply one design to all toes\n * Save your toenail design in your photo album\n * Share your designs easily through Facebook or E-mail with just one click\n * Take a photo with your toenail design as a cover girl\n * Continued improvements of this game, please feel free to send us your feedbacks and suggestionsNeed You Know:\nThis app is totally free to download and play, some basic items are also free to use, but some additional items need you to purchase and pay to unlock. Therefore, if you do not want to use these items, please turn off the in-app purchase in your settings. Thanks."
    ],
