    "description": [
      "A sing-along songbook with more than 100 interactive elements in 3 songs and the little fox music studio! Brought to you by the team that created the bestselling App “Nighty Night”! Great for kids between 2 and 6 years old. HIGHLIGHTS:\n1. Learn popular kids songs!\n2. Stunning designs by Oscar nominated artist Heidi Wittlinger\n3. Play your own music and record your songs with the little fox in his tree house sound studio!\n4. Explore more than 100 interactive elements and sounds!\n5. 3 children’s songs: London Bridge, Evening Song , Old Mac Donald had a farm\n2. The Music Studio full of surprises\n3. Karaoke Mode\n4. Languages: English and GermanLONDON BRIDGE\nLondon is a busy town! Especially since the bridge has a gap. Tourists, a pirate and a parrot, a crocodile, a mermaid and a whale, a cab with a periscope; everything moves and can be touched while the little fox dances behind the windows of the towers.EVENING SONG\nMany animals live in this spectacular night scene; you just have to find them. The owl follows your finger, fascinating ghosts are flying through the air and the stars burst into fireworks. Do you know how to paint with northern lights?OLD MAC DONALD HAD A FARM\nWhile old Mac Donald sleeps under his tree all year, the animals go crazy. Seasons change if you press the button; find out what cow, bee and the young chicks do in summer, spring and winter. How about the little fox? He dresses up as a sheep!MUSIC STUDIO\nBirds, Frogs and dishes sing and jingle! Mommy Fox is knitting to the rhythm and the little fox is dancing. Almost everything in the studio makes a noise, be ready to explore every little corner. FEEDBACK FROM APP USERS:“Little Fox Music Box is the kind of App you wish you had when you were growing up.\" // Famigo “Adorable ! - Cute interactions and message.” / Lovebabbyapps, US\nPRESS:\"The kids that we field tested this app with were enraptured with every aspect and element, and \"WOW-O-WOW\" was heard over and over and over again! This app is beyond anything we have experienced to date.\" // teacherswithapps.com\"I could describe the value of the experience in terms of early music education. I could describe the meticulous design of the app, even down to the music when the credits are rolling. I could continue to wax eloquent. But words fail me. Really, you have to be there. So go there. Get the app.\nJust one word of warning – hide the iPad from your children until you’ve had plenty of play time of your own. If you don’t, it may be many years before you see this app again.\" // Gill Robins ipadappreviewsby.gillrobins.com\"This is a real work of craft\" // guardian.co.uk\"I downloaded Little Fox Music Box last night and my very active 18-month year old daughter (who doesn’t typically stay still for longer than 15 seconds) sat on my lap laughing, clapping, and interacting with the scenes for at least 30 minutes and wasn’t ready to stop(....)It´s a fantastic app!\" // Leanna Loft imore.com ---------If you experience any trouble with the App or have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us any time: contact@foxandsheep.com . We´d love to help you out. Please also mention your device version and your Android version. “Little Fox Music Box” fan? Check out our other Apps at www.foxandsheep.com."
    ],
