    "description": [
      "The Red Bull F1™ Spy will bring you closer to the real action in Formula One. Get insider access and witty observations, live track updates and race stats as well as a load more F1 facts and figures.★★★★„This app keeps you up to date with all the red bull associated inks happening in f1, I would really recommend it, fab!!!!!!“ ★★★★★★★★ TOP10 in ‘Sports’ in Germany, UK, Japan and many more! ★★★★− Are you looking for more insight than your TV-broadcast could ever deliver?\n− Want to know what’s going on in the F1 Paddock and to see behind the scenes?\n− Have you been looking for a knowledgeable expert during races?All insights are brought to you by current F1 world champions’ man on the inside, this one gives you everything, from results to parties, from behind-the-scenes pictures to gossip.REAL-TIME COMMENTARY\nFollow every race with real-time commentary from our spy on the inside and get all the insights you need. CHALLENGE THE SPY\nAsk our Spy anything F1-related or challenge him. It’s essential for any F1 fan who wants a little more information than the average spectator – or who secretly loves a bit of grand prix gossip.TEAM DIARY\nStay up to date with everything the team does, both during races and in between. Get all the news and gossip and with our calendar sync you will never miss a session again. Nice, eh?RACE GRAPHICS\nAll the facts and figures plus local trivia all delivered in one neat graphic for your viewing pleasure.RACE DATA\nEnjoy live track updates, race stats as well as drivers and constructors standings. ★ FEATURES\n− Real time commentary from our spy\n− All the latest news and gossip\n− Team Diary\n− Exclusive behind-the-scenes pictures\n− Challenge the spy! #SpyChallenge\n− Full race results\n− Driver and constructor championship standings\n− Calendar-sync for the F1-sessions\nIf you have any ideas on how we could further improve this app then please let us know!\n support@redbull.com More on Red Bull Racing:\n http://www.redbullracing.com or on Facebook:\n https://www.facebook.com/redbullracing"
    ],
