    "description": [
      "The Whole Pantry is the first of its kind, combining inspiring wholefood with Lifestyle and Wellness Guides.\nWith guide contributions from some of the worlds most inspiring and respected innovators, and the promise to be regularly updating – We aim to provide our community and users with new tools, recipes and encouragement to live their whole lives.We don’t want to convert anyone from one diet or lifestyle to another, but rather encourage more of the basic foods (fruits and veggies) back into our diets where possible. We have a ‘back to basics’ approach to both cooking and nutrition, so we’ve kept sugar, grains and gluten out, dairy to a minimum and the promise of a wholefood diet and its benefits high. Our meals are all created with its benefits in mind, to improve sleep, lose weight, clear skin, reduce allergies, better digestion or balance moods – we’ve got it covered!Recipe and Guide updates each month!•52 premium recipes (entirely gluten free, vegetarian paleo and vegan friendly)\n•10 health, wellness and lifestyle guides\n•Recommended - A resources list of favourite books, blogs, website and documentaries (non interactive)\n•Leading design, photography and interface\n•Shopping list - email to your phone\n•Multiple photos for each recipe\n•Recipe indicators\n•Conversion tool\n•Save your favourite recipes and guides\n•Share what you’ve been cooking or reading with your friends\n•Monthly updates!We really care about the Earth, its communities and their local environments. We think everyone who has access to our app is in a privileged position, so part of the sale from your TWP app purchase goes towards rotating charities and organizations that support the health and wellbeing of those globally, protecting and conserving the environment and giving education to those who otherwise don’t have the opportunity. Thank you to everyone who supported Belle’s journey with cancer and on her path to health. We hope this app gives you some of the support or inspiration you need, whichever path you’re on!"
    ],
