      "Start earning points to redeem for prizes and sweepstakes entries by just going about your day! Install the Panel App - Rewards and Prizes, register for the Points Panel, and see the points increase every morning!The Panel App collects your location data, and in exchange, lets you earn points for prizes including gift cards for Amazon, Visa, Redbox, Google Play and more. Earn bonus points by completing surveys, connecting your social networks and referring your friends.\nGuaranteed Prizes for September include:\n- $2 and $5 Amazon Gift Cards\n- $2 and $5 Cash Via PayPal\nThe Panel App gives you the option to redeem points for sweepstakes entries or a guaranteed prize. The guaranteed prizes have \"GUARANTEED\" in front of the prize name. When you redeem for the guaranteed prize, you will be emailed the gift card on the Monday following the day you redeem. The September Sweepstakes includes:Drawn on Tuesdays:\n-Six (6) - $5 Amazon Gift Cards\n-Five (5) - $5 PayPal Cash\n-Six (6) - $10 Amazon Gift Cards\n-Five (5) - $10 PayPal Cash\n-Ten (10) - Free Movie Rentals from RedboxDrawn on October 1st:\n-Three (3) - $10 Starbucks Gift Cards\n-One (1) - $15 Gamestop Gift Card\n-One (1) - $15 AMC Theatres Gift Card\n-One (1) - $15 Domino’s Gift Card\n-One (1) - $20 Lowe’s Gift Card\n-One (1) - $25 Google Play Gift Card\n-One (1) - $25 Kohl’s Gift Card\n-Four (4) - $25 Visa Gift Cards\n-One (1) - $25 Amazon Gift Cards\n-One (1) - $25 PayPal Cash\n-Six (6) - $50 Visa Gift Cards\n-Three (3) - $50 Amazon Gift Card\n-Two (2) - $50 PayPal CashGuaranteed gift cards will be emailed to you the Monday after you redeem. The drawings for the $5 and $10 Amazon gift cards and PayPal Cash, and the free Redbox rentals will be held on Tuesdays. All other sweepstakes prizes will be awarded on October 1st. Winners will be notified by email and will also be listed at: http://www.facebook.com/PanelApplication .\nThe Panel App collects location data for the purpose of analytics and reporting. Location data is pooled with data collected from thousands of panelists to provide meaningful insights to third parties about the population at large. Analytics and reporting are limited to aggregates of multiple users, and not available at the individual level to third parties. This data is not used for ad targeting. Opt out at any time by uninstalling the app.\nLike the Panel App on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/PanelApplication\nFollow the Panel App on Twitter: https://twitter.com/panel_app"
